* Carnage growled low but kept her temper in check, she needed this clone to 
help her beat the slag out of Megatron. She looked at the clone then past 
her, there was nothing there! But it was then that she remembered.
Carnage looked back at Cyber Claw...*

* The Maximals ran into a little trouble the last time I was here. Their 
base, or what's left of it, is now under 20 feet of water below where it 
originally was."

* Carnage walked past Cyber Claw and began to make her way towards the area 
where the old ship was, her scanners were detecting active signatures but 
they were way beyond where the ship used to be. In order to get to them she 
had to pass the old site and make her way over the last few clicks, they 
were close but not too close. It would still take a day and a half to reach 
the place where she was picking up the energy signatures.
Carnage sighed, more traveling!
She gestured with her head for the others to follow and called back...*

" Come on!"
